{
  "stem": "8703.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a matter of fact, my brother--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was among them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother Harry was among them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the last minute, our good friend, who was also active in, in the Judenrat, Yosl Kleinert, he survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took him out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And thanks to him, my brother survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they, they kept them until [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when-- until before-- they killed them just at the same time as we-- when they liquidated Chmielnik.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The liquidation of-- well, before liquidation, I would like to say something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "October the 1st, 1942--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They organized-- they were calling everyone from, from 16 to 40, men and women, to come to the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's-- there will be a selection for, for-- to send-- they didn't say where and when.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody has to report to the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Judenrat made this announcement, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everybody--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there, it was an open ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a closed ghetto like in Lodz--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because most of the people were, were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were all over the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What we had to do is to close the front entrances and close-- border up all the windows, all the doors, not to go in or out through the main street--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--where it was facing, the window or the doors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had to go out through the back street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- yes, we remained in our home, only through the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the main street, a Jew was not allowed to go there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- this was the creation of the ghetto before--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This creation of the ghetto was in, in April of 1941.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the center became not the main streets, but the side streets--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--where they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People stayed the same home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the problem was, it became so crowded.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
